## Description (4000 characters max)

DreamLens is your personal AI dream interpreter that works entirely on your device. Describe your dream, tap a button, and receive a rich interpretation — all without an internet connection and without your data ever leaving your phone.

AN AI THAT LIVES ON YOUR DEVICE
DreamLens uses a compact yet powerful AI model (Qwen 3.5) that is bundled directly inside the app. There are no servers, no API calls, no cloud processing. The moment you download the app, everything is ready to go — even in airplane mode.

HOW IT WORKS
• Write down your dream in your own words
• Tap "Decode Dream" and let the AI analyze it
• Get a detailed interpretation with emotional tone, key symbols, and a unique dream aura visualization
• Your dream is saved to your personal journal automatically

RICH INTERPRETATIONS
Every dream analysis includes:
— Emotional Tone: the dominant emotion of your dream, identified with an emoji
— Symbols: key elements from your dream and what they may represent
— Interpretation: a 2-3 sentence analysis of your dream's meaning
— Dream Aura: a unique animated color visualization generated from your dream

THREE INTERPRETATION STYLES
Choose how you want your dreams interpreted:
• Mystical — a spiritual, symbolic approach rooted in ancient traditions
• Scientific — a psychological perspective inspired by dream research
• Poetic — a literary, artistic reading of your dream's narrative

DREAM JOURNAL
All your interpreted dreams are saved in a beautiful card-based timeline. Revisit any dream to read its full interpretation, symbols, and aura. Delete entries you no longer need.

BILINGUAL AI
The AI can interpret your dreams in English or Russian. Switch languages anytime in Settings — your next interpretation will be in the language you choose.

DESIGNED FOR THE NIGHT
DreamLens features a dark cosmic interface with animated starfields, glassmorphism cards, and smooth animations. It's designed to feel calm and immersive — perfect for those moments right after you wake up.

YOUR PRIVACY IS ABSOLUTE
• No internet connection required — ever
• No accounts, no sign-ups, no logins
• No data is collected, transmitted, or shared
• No analytics, no tracking, no ads
• Dreams are stored only on your device as local files
• Delete the app and all data is gone

REQUIREMENTS
• iPhone 12 or newer (A14 Bionic chip or later)
• iOS 17.0 or later
• Approximately 600 MB of storage space

